xxl.applications.pipes.traffic
Class Vehicle

java.lang.Object
  xxl.applications.pipes.traffic.Vehicle

public class Vehicle
extends Object

An instance of this class contains information about one tuple generated by a highway sensor (http://www.clearingstelle-verkehr.de/cs/verkehrsdaten/katalog/katalogberichte/fsp/fsp_metadaten).

Field Summary
protected  char direction
          the direction of the highway usually n or s (where n stands for north and s for south).
protected  int distanceToCity
          the distance from the sensor to the city marina.

          the lane of the sensor (usually between 1 and 5).
protected  double length
